According to the Prosecutor ' s Office, funds obtained in public tenders were used for their own purposes by justifying on many occasions the performance of tasks with false invoices.
The public funds and that of the municipalities - in their entirety about 65 million HUF - partially stopped in the treasury of the Fial Baloldal organization and in part in the pocket of private persons.
The method, which was also revealed by the researchers, was to justify the collection of the funds obtained in public tenders with false invoices behind which there was no real execution, the various associations never fulfilled their obligations assumed.
