He requested invoices for his consumption, and they served as a model to make the invoices that were presented among others in the contests of the Ministry of Youth and Sports Affairs, the Ministry of Social and Labour Affairs, as well as in the City of Capital.
These invoices were mostly signed by István Lados and his accomplice András ★ri, who according to our information rather wrote the reports necessary to obtain the public subsidies.
